Package com

Class Hotel

java.lang.Object
com.Hotel
public class Hotel extends Object
Represents a Hotel with a name, a list of rooms, and a list of reservations.

    • showVoucherRoom

      public int showVoucherRoom(String guestName, String checkInStr, String checkOutStr)
      Validates the voucher room details based on guest name and check-in/check-out dates.
      Parameters:
      guestName - the name of the guest
      checkInStr - the check-in date as a string
      checkOutStr - the check-out date as a string
      Returns:
      a result code indicating the validation status: 0 - valid, 1 - guest name is missing, 2 - check-in or check-out date is invalid, 3 - check-in date is out of range, 4 - check-out date is out of range, 5 - check-in date is not before check-out date
